<h1>Fermi Paradox</h1>
<small>The content on this page has been referenced from <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fermi_paradox">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fermi_paradox</a></small>
<hr>
<em>This article is about the absence of evidence for extraterrestrial intelligence. For the type of estimation problem, see <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fermi_problem">Fermi problem</a>. For the Tub Ring album, see <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fermi_Paradox_(album)">Fermi Paradox (album)</a>.</em>
